\end_inset

, which is an integer with 
\begin_inset Formula $239$
\end_inset

 digits.
 For the Boolean case, the study of the equation (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.3.1"

\end_inset

) leads us to the demonstration of the cusick conjecture, Li and Stanica
