S_{\mathbb{F}_{q}}(F)=\sum_{{\bf x}\in\mathbb{F}_{q}^{n}}e^{\frac{2\pi i}{p}\text{Tr}_{\mathbb{F}_{q}/\mathbb{F}_{p}}(F({\bf x}))},
